cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a deep learning solution for characterizing driving styles using GPS data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) as GPS data is a type of image data. The paper also involves feature extraction and pattern recognition, which are common topics in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses the security and privacy implications of the proposed approach, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper involves the use of real-world datasets, which is a common topic in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
